data.title: Cadence Animal Hospital
data.text:
Dr. Brenna Ledezma is a dedicated veterinarian hailing from the charming town of La Porte, Texas. Her journey into the world of veterinary medicine began at Texas A&M University, where she pursued both her undergraduate and veterinary studies.

With a passion for ensuring the well-being of animals, Dr. Ledezmaâ€™s professional interests lie in the fields of Dermatology and Dentistry. She is deeply committed to providing the highest standard of care for her furry patients, always striving to improve their quality of life.

Beyond her veterinary endeavors, Dr. Ledezma finds joy in spending quality time with her beloved family and indulging in her passion for baking. At home, she shares her life with her pets: 3 dogs and 4 cats- 1 Siamese and 3 orange tabbys.
